    {
      "text": "The fifth numbered game in the Kawa no Nushi Tsuri / Legend of the River King series.\nThe game is a Fishing Role Playing Game in which you aim to get better rods and gear to be able to catch bigger and more elusive fish.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Keita visits his grandfather's house during the summer vacation. Upon arrival he hears a rumour that the nearby swamp is cursed, causing the people of the town to turn into fish. It is said that only a legendary fisherman can break the curse and save the people. And so Keita begins fishing...",
